Adding SessionManager2, a new interface which has a launchForRun method, which will be called from FB in the case of run launches. This is being added to enable termination of run launches. launchForRun returns the systemProcess that is created for the launch. PlayerSessionManager and ThreadSafeSessionManager now implement SessionManager2 which extends SessionManager. ProcessListener has been modified to block "application already running" notification to the user.
